    </div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="carousel-item">
    <div class="review-card rounded-box">
      <div class="avatar">
        <div class="rounded-full">
          <%= image_tag "mike.jpg", alt: "Mike D." %>
          <strong>Mike D.</strong>
          <div class="stars">
            &#9733; &#9733; &#9733; &#9733; &#9733;
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p>"This app is exactly what I needed to track the connection between what I eat and how I feel. Since I started using it, I’ve noticed a huge improvement in managing my heart rate and energy levels. The interface is user-friendly and the tips are incredibly helpful. A must-have for anyone taking charge of their health!"</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="carousel-item">
    <div class="review-card rounded-box">
      <div class="avatar">
        <div class="rounded-full">
          <%= image_tag "aaron.jpg", alt: "Aaron M." %>
          <strong>Aaron M.</strong>
          <div class="stars">
            &#9733; &#9733; &#9733; &#9733; &#9733;
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p>"Great app for health enthusiasts and anyone needing to monitor specific health markers. It’s so helpful to see the direct impact of different foods on my blood glucose and overall wellness. The detailed analytics and customization options make it an invaluable tool for personal health management."</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="carousel-item">
    <div class="review-card rounded-box">
      <div class="avatar">
        <div class="rounded-full">
          <%= image_tag "james.jpg", alt: "James P." %>
          <strong>James P.</strong>
          <div class="stars">
            &#9733; &#9733; &#9733; &#9733; &#9733;
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p>"I've been using this app for a few months now, and it's fantastic for anyone with food sensitivities or anyone who just wants to understand their body better. Tracking my meals and symptoms has helped me identify foods that were causing discomfort that I wasn’t aware of before. The app is intuitive and packed with useful features!"</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="carousel-item">
    <div class="review-card rounded-box">
      <div class="avatar">
        <div class="rounded-full">
          <%= image_tag "https://daisyui.com/images/stock/photo-1534528741775-53994a69daeb.jpg", alt: "Lily T." %>
          <strong>Lily T.</strong>
          <div class="stars">
            &#9733; &#9733; &#9733; &#9733; &#9733;
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p>"This app has revolutionized the way I manage my diet and health. Tracking my food intake and observing how it affects my symptoms has empowered me to make better decisions about what I eat. The app is not only functional but also beautifully designed, making the process of logging and reviewing data a pleasure."</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>


